import React from "react"
import {
  ChakraProvider,
  CSSReset,
  Box,
    Text,
    IconButton,
    useColorMode,
    Flex,
    Link,
  } from "@chakra-ui/react"
 

const LeftSideBar = () => {
  const { colorMode } = useColorMode();

  return(
    <ChakraProvider>
      <CSSReset />
    <Box
      w="100%"
      h="100vh"
      bg={colorMode === "light" ? "gray.100" : "gray.800"}
    >
      <Flex
        direction="column"
        align="center"
        justify="center"
        h="100%"
      >
        <IconButton icon={<settingsIcon />} />
        <Text mt={4}>Settings</Text>
        <Link mt={6}>Link 1</Link>
        <Link mt={2}>Link 2</Link>
      </Flex>
    </Box>
    </ChakraProvider>
  )
}

export default LeftSideBar;
